      <tr>
        <td>1</td>
        <td><strong>Pipedrive</strong></td>
        <td>$14/mo</td>
        <td>4.5/5</td>
        <td>Sales-focused SMBs needing visual pipeline management</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>2</td>
        <td><strong>Monday CRM</strong></td>
        <td>$12/mo</td>
        <td>4.3/5</td>
        <td>Teams already using Monday.com for project management</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>3</td>
        <td><strong>Freshsales</strong></td>
        <td>$0/mo</td>
        <td>4.4/5</td>
        <td>Small businesses wanting built-in phone, email, and chat</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>4</td>
        <td><strong>Zoho CRM</strong></td>
        <td>$0/mo</td>
        <td>4.3/5</td>
        <td>Budget-conscious SMBs wanting feature-rich CRM</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>5</td>
        <td><strong>Close</strong></td>
        <td>$29/mo</td>
        <td>4.6/5</td>
        <td>Inside sales teams relying on phone and email outreach</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>


  <div class="tool-card" id="pipedrive">
    <h3>#1 Pipedrive — $14/mo</h3>
    <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Sales-focused SMBs needing visual pipeline management</p>
    <p><strong>Why switch from HubSpot CRM:</strong> Best-in-class visual pipeline management</p>
    <ul>
      <li>3,000 open deals</li>
      <li>Visual pipeline (drag-and-drop)</li>
      <li>Email sync</li>
      <li>30 automation workflows</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="pros-cons">
      <div class="pros"><h4>Pros</h4><ul><li>Best-in-class visual pipeline management</li><li>Very intuitive and fast to set up</li><li>Strong automation even at mid-tier</li></ul></div>
      <div class="cons"><h4>Cons</h4><ul><li>No free plan</li><li>Limited marketing features</li></ul></div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://pipedrive.pxf.io/stackpick" class="cta-button" rel="nofollow sponsored">Try Pipedrive →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="tool-card" id="monday-crm">
    <h3>#2 Monday CRM — $12/mo</h3>
    <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Teams already using Monday.com for project management</p>
    <p><strong>Why switch from HubSpot CRM:</strong> Highly visual and customizable</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Unlimited contacts</li>
      <li>Unlimited pipelines</li>
      <li>Email integration</li>
      <li>Activity management</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="pros-cons">
      <div class="pros"><h4>Pros</h4><ul><li>Highly visual and customizable</li><li>Strong PM integration for post-sale workflows</li><li>Generous automation limits on Pro</li></ul></div>
      <div class="cons"><h4>Cons</h4><ul><li>3-seat minimum increases entry cost</li><li>CRM features less mature than dedicated tools</li></ul></div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://monday.com/stackpick" class="cta-button" rel="nofollow sponsored">Try Monday CRM →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="tool-card" id="freshsales">
