    <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Small businesses wanting built-in phone, email, and chat</p>
    <p><strong>Why switch from HubSpot CRM:</strong> Built-in multichannel communication</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Contact management</li>
      <li>Built-in phone/email/chat</li>
      <li>AI contact scoring (Freddy AI)</li>
      <li>Visual pipeline</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="pros-cons">
      <div class="pros"><h4>Pros</h4><ul><li>Built-in multichannel communication</li><li>AI-powered lead scoring</li><li>Clean, modern interface</li></ul></div>
      <div class="cons"><h4>Cons</h4><ul><li>Smaller integration ecosystem</li><li>Advanced reporting only in Pro+</li></ul></div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://freshworks.com/stackpick" class="cta-button" rel="nofollow sponsored">Try Freshsales →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="tool-card" id="zoho-crm">
    <h3>#4 Zoho CRM — $0/mo</h3>
    <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Budget-conscious SMBs wanting feature-rich CRM</p>
    <p><strong>Why switch from HubSpot CRM:</strong> Excellent value at every tier</p>
    <ul>
      <li>5,000 records (free)</li>
      <li>Multiple pipelines</li>
      <li>Scoring rules</li>
      <li>Workflows</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="pros-cons">
      <div class="pros"><h4>Pros</h4><ul><li>Excellent value at every tier</li><li>Deep integration with 45+ Zoho apps</li><li>Zia AI for predictions and suggestions</li></ul></div>
      <div class="cons"><h4>Cons</h4><ul><li>UI can feel dated</li><li>Steep learning curve</li></ul></div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://www.zoho.com/crm/stackpick" class="cta-button" rel="nofollow sponsored">Try Zoho CRM →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="tool-card" id="close">
    <h3>#5 Close — $29/mo</h3>
    <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Inside sales teams relying on phone and email outreach</p>
    <p><strong>Why switch from HubSpot CRM:</strong> Best-in-class built-in calling</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pipeline view</li>
      <li>Built-in calling (power dialer)</li>
      <li>SMS</li>
      <li>Email sequences</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="pros-cons">
      <div class="pros"><h4>Pros</h4><ul><li>Best-in-class built-in calling</li><li>Designed for outbound/inside sales</li><li>Email sequences and SMS built in</li></ul></div>
      <div class="cons"><h4>Cons</h4><ul><li>Significantly more expensive at higher tiers</li><li>No free plan</li></ul></div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://close.com/stackpick" class="cta-button" rel="nofollow sponsored">Try Close →</a>
  </div>

  <h2>Why Look for HubSpot CRM Alternatives?</h2>
  <p>While HubSpot CRM is a solid crm software tool rated 4.5/5, it's not perfect for everyone. Common reasons to switch:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Steep pricing jump to Professional ($90/user/mo)</li>
    <li>Advanced workflows locked behind paid tiers</li>
    <li>Per-seat minimums on higher plans</li>
  </ul>

